children.description: Given than Juan wants to sign up to the uTest site
Juan open up
Juan opens the U test page
Juan clicks on Button that shows us the Join Today button

When he fills out the signup form
| strFirstName | strLastName | strEmail | strMonthOfBirth | strDayOfBirth | strYearOfBirth | strPassword | strConfirmPassword |
| Juan David | Botero | soundga22@yahoo.es | number:1 | 12 | 1999 | Martinez1985++ | Martinez1985++ |
Juan registration
Juan enters 'Juan David' into Where the user writes their first name
Juan enters 'Botero' into Where the user writes their last name
Juan enters 'soundga22@yahoo.es' into Where the user writes their email
Juan enters 'number:1' into Where the user selects their birth month
Juan enters '12' into Where the user writes their birth day
Juan enters '1999' into Where the user writes their birth year
Juan clicks on Button that shows us the next signup form page
Juan clicks on Button that shows us the next signup form page
Juan clicks on Button that shows us the last signup form page
Juan enters 'Martinez1985++' into Where the user writes their password
Juan enters 'Martinez1985++' into Where the user confirms their password
Juan clicks on Where the user accepts the uTest Terms of Use
Juan clicks on Where the user accepts the uTest Privacy Policy
Juan clicks on Button that completes the setup

Then he has registered on the website and receives a message
| strMessage |
| Welcome to the world's largest community of freelance software testers! |
